{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"de928491bd","title":"致班禅额尔德尼电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"829f0b8a96","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":13,"articleId":"de928491bd"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"667b5d52d9","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"班禅额尔德尼，即班禅额尔德尼·确吉坚赞，西藏宗教领袖之一，当时准备由青海玉树返回西藏日喀则地区。"},{"id":"a6861cf398","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"达赖喇嘛，即达赖喇嘛·丹增嘉措，西藏宗教领袖之一。"},{"id":"b01810118e","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"和平解放西藏办法的协议，即1951年5月23日在北京签订的《中央人民政府和西藏地方政府关于和平解放西藏办法的协议》"}],"contents":[{"id":"f3edfd0014","type":"title","text":"致班禅额尔德尼\"电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd"},{"id":"667b5d52d9","type":"paragraph","text":"青海省人民政府转班禅额尔德尼先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd"},{"id":"a6861cf398","type":"paragraph","text":"感谢你的来电。我完全同意你的这种志愿，即在中国共产党和中央人民政府领导下，与达赖喇嘛紧密团结，为彻底实行和平解放西藏办法的协议，驱除帝国主义在西藏的影响，巩固国防和建设新西藏而奋斗。并祝你顺利地到达目的地","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd"},{"id":"b01810118e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd"},{"id":"31e022f641","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十二月十三日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd"}],"page":{"id":"ddfccd2d13","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"de928491bd","start":138,"end":138}}}},"__N_SSG":true}